hopobject.body: It's a bad line saba xtreme 5000 for sale But in the end, emotion is offset by the excitement of a more efficient camp, especially for a technologically-savvy coach like Kelly. Case in point: Kelly and his staff will have their practice filmed with high-definition cameras, downloaded and ready to watch as soon as the team steps off the NovaCare Complex practice fields, whereas there would normally be lag time for the footage to download at Lehigh. Seconds matter to Kelly during the work day, so minutes would surely be agonizing for him.
